_sText:
<fieldset> Hosties_dust-fun by -[Element]- </fieldset>

<fieldset> This map I made becuase, a lot of people randomly started getting into hosties, and didn't have many maps to play, so I made this for a variety of maps to have, it has custom skybox and a few custom textures, this map has, imo, everything a good hosties map should have. THis map has the following ;

-Chicken Fight and knife fight cage on roof
-Shot for shot and racing in the back
-Jump shot around CT spawn
-6 Big cells that can hold many T's ( only open from inside )
-A cage where the Ct's can keep T's and check for guns
-Lots of rebeling spots
-A big building with many rooms
-And much, much more!
</fieldset>

<fieldset>
